{"tid":1625100,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"外交部：堅決支持香港特區政府制訂《禁止蒙面規例》","createTime":"2019-10-05T05:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T11:04:51.000Z","uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4ea9c44cdd34607c5287786688541239a682e6b4","tid":1625100,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:51:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/393304404377707/posts/959758577732284/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F393304404377707%2Fposts%2F959758577732284%2F&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KBnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=7cba5c2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/393304404377707/posts/959758577732284/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zykMAMc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzykMAMc.jpg&h=145a1812&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【堅決支持香港特區政府制訂《禁止蒙面規例》！】<br />\n<br />\n當前香港面臨的最大危險是暴力橫行、法治不彰。在此情況下，特區政府制訂《禁止蒙面規例》，合法合理合情，極爲必要！<br />\n<br />\n堅決支持林鄭月娥行政長官、特區政府和警隊、司法機構依法採取一切必要措施懲治所有暴力犯罪分子，特别是那些暴力犯罪的骨幹分子及其背後的策劃者、組織者、指揮者，以彰顯法律的公正與威嚴！<br />\n<br />\n----------<br />\n<br />\n歡迎關注公署官方微信公眾號(帳號:fmcoprc)，希望為你提供豐富有益的資訊和便捷周到的服務。"},{"pid":"26ac86da3ae0dd9fff2185ed8025949c837d6551","tid":1625100,"uid":25108,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:52:30.000Z","msg":"基本法第22條：中央人民政府所屬各部門、各省、自治區、直轄市均不得干預香港特別行政區根據本法自行管理的事務。"},{"pid":"b20da0e62a81ec7b53fdff3f5b54e81d54f2a6c1","tid":1625100,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f228cf0669fd90e23e99ea7aec9579b9e92efa5","tid":1625100,"uid":